{"tid":304072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個兩老古怪習慣","createTime":"2017-06-30T15:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T15:54:45.000Z","uid":91601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d922b6013b481f7554b9b2be239d246b9c165ca","tid":304072,"uid":91601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"我老豆唔知點解可以由朝到晚都係開住新聞台不斷睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同一單新聞可以睇幾次，仲可以若無其事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我地睇唔到其他台，睇到我背返份稿出黎都仲得<br />\n口頭上話過佢好多次，但佢都可以㩒返新聞台繼續睇<br />\n明明朝早佢又有睇報紙 其他台又有更好既野睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37152e6c4c5ad04d943cbd1a278315ba1ea8ea21","tid":304072,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"我會幫佢轉sources 因為佢地唔識轉"}]}